      • dimension

        public static Dimension dimension​(int D)
        Returns the Dimension instance for the "pressure" appropriate to the given dimension. In particular, for D = 3, returns Pressure.DIMENSION; for D = 2, returns Pressure2D.DIMENSION.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if D is not equal to 2, or 3.
